Premium Shape NestOne (Sarang Burung Walet Utuh)

The Swallow’s Nest built by aerodramus swiftlets. The colours are ivory-white and white. Whole swallow nests are formed when swallows build their nests in their own swallow nest houses, and will form into triangles when the nest is built in the corner of a room. Whole swallow’s nest is the most perfect form of swallow’s nest and is of high value.

The Value of NestOne Swallow’s Nest:

💯 Natural Processing

🤝 Direct from Our Birdnest House

❤️ High Technology Processing

😇 Food Safety and Guarantee, Ready to Eat

👍 No Chemical, Very Low Nitrit (under 30 PPM)

Did You Know?

NestOne swallow nests are cleaned through a detailed, thorough and hygienic process in a cleaning factory that prioritizes product safety. So don’t worry about consuming NestOne swallow nests 🙂

Purchase Now! 🙂
